definition:
Someone descended from Jachin who was a man of the tribe of Simeon living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.10; 
 son of: Simeon (H8095); 
 brother of: Jemuel (H3223), Jamin (H3226), Ohad (H0161), Zerah (H2226L)  and Shaul (H7586H); also called Jarib at 1Ch.4.24; 
Group of ya.khin (יָכִין "Jachin" H3199) 
 § Jachinites , of Jachin "he will establish"
 the descendants of Jachin
